data.description: This stunning 4BR+ home on the lake boasts a family room and 3 baths, with breathtaking views of the beautiful lake. Although unassuming from the outside, the unique layout of the home becomes apparent as soon as you step inside. Take in the stunning lake views from the screened-in patio or backyard. Adding to its charm is an indoor atrium that is a unique feature within the house. With plenty of entertaining spaces, this spacious home boasts a brand-new air-conditioner and an upgraded 80-gallon water heater, along with recently done landscaping.
